Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.00,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.14,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Father! Mother! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.50,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:08.28,Code 1,,0,0,0,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:11.70,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakura-kun! It looks like you're feeling better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.01,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Yuki-chan's nursing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:18.95,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's because I would do anything for Sakura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.65,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Mother... What was I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:24.85,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:25.45,Code 1,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.21,Code 1,,0,0,0,,So you found me at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:37.26,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It was Daisuke-san who found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.54,Code 1,,0,0,0,,We were so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.61,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You felt so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:44.22,Code 1,,0,0,0,,But it's such a relief that you're well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.56,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Father, Mother, I'm sorry that I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.98,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it will not happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:58.90,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan, both me and your mom are happy as long as your out of harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.80,Code 1,,0,0,0,,That's right Sakura-kun, you're the most important thing to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.97,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Indeed. But I wonder who brought you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.72,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any idea who it might have been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:15.98,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.39,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Bring the wicked to justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.90,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Yes, could you condone such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:40.23,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Whether for revenge or otherwise,\Nthat is not something I can condone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.66,Code 3,,0,0,0,,That's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:52.67,Code 3,,0,0,0,,There aren't even any ashes left...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.51,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Burn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:05.68,Code 3,,0,0,0,,He tried to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:16.17,Code 1,,0,0,0,,But, why did he let me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:42.51,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakura! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.82,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Uh? Yeah, good morning Aoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.78,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Come with me. There's something I want to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.49,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.99,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Are you in a bad mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.55,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Ogami, what are you planning to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.54,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Come on! Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.35,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.79,Code 1,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you're into Ogami-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.66,Code 1,,0,0,0,,you can't just ignore that your best friend is talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:15.68,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Aoba. I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.89,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.43,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You want any advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.25,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's about Ogami-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.02,Code 1,,0,0,0,,The truth is last night, at the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.30,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing, Takatsu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.02,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Are you sharing secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:35.10,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ogami-kun, don't startle us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.20,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:37.52,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You seemed to be enjoying yourselves so much there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.52,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Won't you let me in on the fun too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:45.36,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Hmm, so you're interested in Sakura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.31,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Eh, why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:50.43,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Why else would you butt into our conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:56.76,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.75,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Aoba, don't let him touch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:01.68,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.68,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Don't let him touch you, or you'll burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:07.07,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What's going on? A sudden love triangle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.09,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Is Sakurakouji-san jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.29,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.69,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Not only Sakurakouji-san, but now you're aiming for Aoba-chan too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.82,Code 1,,0,0,0,,A world war this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:18.46,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What are you going on about, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.43,Code 1,,0,0,0,,He just put his hand on my shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.37,Code 1,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.96,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakurakouji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.35,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.45,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Please explain it to me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:30.95,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:37.55,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Bastard... In order to make sure that I don't talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:42.11,Code 3,,0,0,0,,If I say anything to anyone, he'll burn all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.81,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Everyone, sit down please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:47.29,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's time for class!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.25,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakurakouji, hurry up and take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.41,Code 1,,0,0,0,,T-Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.15,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.27,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ah... no, it is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.79,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:24.82,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Seriously, don't leave me behind like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.17,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, Aoba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.81,Code 3,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.80,Code 3,,0,0,0,,If we stick together he'll come after Aoba too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.27,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.80,Code 3,,0,0,0,,I knew it, he's watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.88,Code 3,,0,0,0,,If it goes on like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.28,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.37,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Why are you eating out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.54,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Let's have lunch together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:04.42,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Aoba...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.80,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Aoba! Please get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.26,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Eh, what, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.01,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Get away from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:14.73,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.87,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.94,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you being a bit too mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.30,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I apologize. That was not my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:31.28,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Well. I understand that you're interested in Ogami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.27,Code 1,,0,0,0,,But why are you avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:35.99,Code 1,,0,0,0,,No, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.59,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:41.26,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think, Aoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.89,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.51,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What's the matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.51,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakurakouji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:04.27,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ogami! I have something to say to you in private!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:07.73,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Will you come with me after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.14,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakura never gives up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.31,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's an after-school date!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:15.53,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakurakouji-san, what's so good about that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.78,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:31.67,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Aoba, when this is over, I will tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.80,Code 1,,0,0,0,,So just wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.16,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.59,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.81,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Talk to you later then, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:50.13,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Meow meow Nyanmaru, everybody's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:54.87,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Kind-hearted, always on little kittens side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:59.47,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Fading life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:05.41,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is only enough for one more try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.43,Code 1,,0,0,0,,And there're no more Nyanmarus left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.42,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'll go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.84,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Customer! Don't forget to bring these with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.65,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:14.93,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'll leave them with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.13,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:19.06,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I already saved the Nyanmarus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:23.81,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Putting that aside, if you're gonna burn, what color would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.27,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Eh? Burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:28.09,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'd prefer blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:30.77,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Blue flames are the most beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.96,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be so suspicious of me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:42.45,Code 1,,0,0,0,,So you are aware that you've done things to make me wary of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.04,Code 1,,0,0,0,,By the way, what did you want to speak with me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:53.54,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Meow meow Nyanmaru, everybody's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:58.41,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Kind-hearted, always on little kittens' side. Fading...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.45,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Nyanmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.93,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Nyanmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.94,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Nyanmaru, Nyanmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:29.71,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:30.81,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's your next job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.63,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Code:Breaker - Code: 03,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.56,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Tenpouin Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:48.93,Code 1,,0,0,0,,At a place like this, you will not be able to do anything funny, {They're at Hachikou Station :P}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.44,Code 1,,0,0,0,,with this many people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.41,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Answer me this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:02.36,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Did you killed the G-Falcon thugs with those blue flames?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.14,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Even if you'd try to deny it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:05.78,Code 1,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.54,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I killed them. But, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.80,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to hide it you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.71,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Bastard, do you realize what you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.77,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:27.32,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Also, what's so bad about getting rid of garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:27.86,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:32.16,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Guys like them may exist, but they're of no use to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.40,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Is that why you killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.94,Code 1,,0,0,0,,They were murderers themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.15,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Even so, why would you kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.15,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to be some kind of hero of justice or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.61,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'm quite evil actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.91,Code 1,,0,0,0,,More than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.05,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:52.25,Code 1,,0,0,0,,If you think that, then turn yourself in to the police and atone for your crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.70,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Atone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.73,Code 1,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.84,Code 1,,0,0,0,,If you turn yourself in, your punishment will become lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.17,Code 1,,0,0,0,,The punishment will become lighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.40,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.43,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:14.92,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ogami, do you really understand what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:20.07,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You're taking people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.45,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.09,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.91,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ogami, do you not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:42.00,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Do you not have any regrets for what you have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:44.70,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.76,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Taku-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:52.38,Code 1,,0,0,0,,M-My apologies! It was my fault, I was shouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.62,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.27,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You were looking for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.95,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:12.04,Code 1,,0,0,0,,There, there Taku-chan! What a nice young man that was!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.78,Code 3,,0,0,0,,What kind of person are you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:21.07,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ogami, whatever reasons you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:24.58,Code 1,,0,0,0,,you have no right to pass judgment on people and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.85,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Wait! Just let the law judge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:33.13,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Be judged by the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.91,Code 1,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.28,Code 1,,0,0,0,,The law only judges people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.44,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a non-existent being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.98,Code 1,,0,0,0,,The law can't judge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:54.32,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Even if I burned you along with all these people to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.95,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I would never be convicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.64,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'll erase all the witnessess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.09,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Burn to ashes, Sakurakouji Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.59,Code 3,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:15.47,Code 3,,0,0,0,,In front of all these people, you would burn me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.71,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:22.96,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.25,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.97,Code 1,,0,0,0,,The bag's burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.49,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.30,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Burn to ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:58.06,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.48,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:09.32,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.29,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.73,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I've been observing you all day today, but now there's no question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.33,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You are really one of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.68,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:29.09,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, you killed those people without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:33.64,Code 1,,0,0,0,,And today you had me thinking that you were going to kill me, but now you say you were only observing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.47,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:40.73,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What? The same as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:45.23,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Those G-Falcons killed that homeless man without regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:51.28,Code 1,,0,0,0,,They also hurt other homeless people and even that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:54.66,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You must have thought that their deaths were inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.49,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.49,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Scum like that deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:02.65,Code 1,,0,0,0,,And it's my job to exterminate those kind of vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:06.40,Code 1,,0,0,0,,The evil that judges the evil that the law cannot judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:13.01,Code 1,,0,0,0,,We who do not exist, we are Code: \Breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:16.01,Code 1,,0,0,0,,"Code:Breaker?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:19.63,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You have people you'd like to see dead too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:24.77,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Be honest, tell me the names of those people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.36,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.23,Code 1,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.37,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Unforgiveable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.02,Code 1,,0,0,0,,There is no excuse for killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:36.70,Code 1,,0,0,0,,No matter what kind of person, you cannot just kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.95,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You... Why are you trying so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:46.76,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.34,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:18:00.75,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You can observe me all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:03.14,Code 1,,0,0,0,,But I also will be keeping an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.72,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I swear by my name, Sakurakouji Sakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:09.56,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I will follow you everywhere to make sure that you do not kill anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.19,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You better be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.97,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.24,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'm cracking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.42,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You're really amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.75,Code 1,,0,0,0,,That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.56,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Just remember this:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.25,Code 1,,0,0,0,,If you tell anyone about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:35.51,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I will kill not only you, but also those you tell and all the people around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.26,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I will not let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.81,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:51.67,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.84,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.43,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Whenever, wherever, whoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:02.74,Code 1,,0,0,0,,With no exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:06.75,Code 1,,0,0,0,,I'll burn them beyond ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.32,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Do you think something has happened to Sakura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.97,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Why won't she tell us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:34.15,Code 3,,0,0,0,,You can't stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:39.21,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:42.91,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Those eyes completely devoid of hesitation even while killing.  {Shes says "あの目。何のためらいもなく人を殺めるとき。あの目。"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.45,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Ogami, trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.99,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Exterminate vermin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.84,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Then, what about that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.84,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that you killed Dog with those same cold eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:20:01.82,Code 3,,0,0,0,,Ogami, what did your eyes look like then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:19.81,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Is this going to be all right to include someone like Ogami Rei in our plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:24.44,Code 1,,0,0,0,,He's not easy to deal with, but once you know how to handle him, his results are top notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:28.33,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've arranged for a safety net.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:33.70,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It is set up to activate, should we ever lose control of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.83,Code 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:42.34,Code 1,,0,0,0,,It's about Sakurakouji Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.74,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, I decided not to dispose of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.66,Code 1,,0,0,0,,She's a Chinshu, a "Rare Kind." She's too valuable to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:51.85,Code 1,,0,0,0,,A Rare Kind? Could she really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.58,Code 1,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.39,Code 1,,0,0,0,,That woman, she won't burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:00.11,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Not even by my flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:41.16,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, why did you show up out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:43.17,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Weren't you supposed to be hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:46.22,Code 1,,0,0,0,,To put an end to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:49.09,Code 1,,0,0,0,,And killing people off is your way of doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:52.90,Code 1,,0,0,0,,And you're looking forward to a future with a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:54.43,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You've really grown up. {Sounds like he's saying "バイト未来の君が率先してやってくれなんて。成長したね。"}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:01.07,Code 1,,0,0,0,,However, I thought Ogami-kun would be the first one to come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:02.19,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Wait just a sec No. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:12.12,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Are you planning on passing judgement on me, Yuuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:22.08,Code 1,,0,0,0,,An eye for an eye, a tooth for a tooth, and the requiem of fury for the wicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:29.38,Code 1,,0,0,0,,Next time, Code:Breaker Episode 03,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:31.72,Code 1,,0,0,0,,"Enraged Bravery and Engraved Paths."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:35.68,Code 1,,0,0,0,,You vermin, I will burn you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:39.20,Code 1,,0,0,0,,until not even a speck of ash remains.{All I can make out is "いっぺんのちりすらんのくさせん燃やししつくす", which I can't really make sense of.}
